<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 22:31:54 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5ff351719e7</link><description>&lt;p&gt;加利福尼亚州尤里卡，2026年6月&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Trees!" height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sergio/6a5ff351719e7.jpg" width="5712"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sergio.some.pics"&gt;@sergio&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 22:31:54 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5fafc15e7b4</link><description>&lt;p&gt;那中间的柔软时刻。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="White and grey clouds on a mostly blue sky." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a5fafc15e7b4.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 17:43:31 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5fa06b419a4</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一个有着令人惊叹的前门和防空洞标志的当地商铺。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A local business with an amazing front door and bomb shelter sign. " height="4000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/digitalsnow/6a5fa06b419a4.jpg" width="3000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://digitalsnow.some.pics"&gt;@digitalsnow&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 16:38:07 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5f7e1fd4772</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这是一座大约建于1220年的古老石头教堂的内部。长椅和讲坛是在宗教改革之后，大约在16至17世纪期间安装的。更多信息请参见#AltText。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="The interior of an old stone church dating from the 13th century. The room is lit only by two large windows in the nave and two smaller ones in the choir – one beside and one behind the altar. All are outside the frame. The floor is covered with timber dating from the 15th century. There are wooden pews on both sides, and a wooden crucifix (approximately from the 12th-century) hangs between the nave and the choir. To the side stands a pulpit, from 1579. The altar consists of a 13th-century altar front in the icon style (figures surrounded by gold leaf) and a wooden altarpiece showing the last supper, from 1699. The altar itself is made of stone. Light from the entrance behind the photographer and indirect light from the right-hand side of the altar make the gold on the altar front gleam. A small sailing ship hangs from the ceiling at the front. This was apparently a tradition in Norwegian churches, after the reformation. It is supposed to point towards the altar, but it points to the left (north) instead. The walls are whitewashed. As the church has neither electricity nor running water, the interior has been surprisingly well preserved." height="2778" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a5f7e1fd4772.jpg" width="2168"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 14:11:47 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5ee14f87954</link><description>&lt;p&gt;帕特拉&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Cachorro dorme com almofada " height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sergio/6a5ee14f87954.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sergio.some.pics"&gt;@sergio&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 03:02:43 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>